  "content": "<div>  •  Reinforces thematic literary decay—nothing lasts forever.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> 4. One-Shot Actions (High Risk, High Reward)</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> Certain actions are irreversible &amp permanently change the player’s status.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> One-time sacrifices, betrayals, or high-stakes gambits.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Success grants massive rewards.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Failure locks players out of certain mechanics.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Example: High-Stakes One-Shot Actions</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Action</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Effect (Success)</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Effect (Failure)</div>",
